	<h1 class="question">What is Holiday Planner?</h1>
	<p class="answer">Holiday Planner is an amazing application that
		allows you to plan your holiday perfectly. It helps catering in a plan
		that suits your budget and time. With Holiday Planner, go on an
		amazing journey and explore lands that are both far and near.
		Currently, only one plan can be developed at a time</p>

	<h1 class="question">How to use Holiday Planner?</h1>
	<p class="answer">To use Holiday Planner, you have to log into the
		application. If you do not have an account, sign yourself up with your
		email and password. Once you login, you are exposed to a lot of
		opportunities to plan your trip.</p>
	<p class="answer">> Search for a city (or) submit a form to load in
		the suggestions for a city of your liking.</p>
	<p class="answer">
		> Once you are directed to the city page, click <b>Add Location</b> to
		add the location to your plan.
	</p>
	<p class="answer">
		> If you wish for the application to generate a plan for you, click on
		the <b>Generate Plan</b>.
	</p>
	<p class="answer">
		> Once you have decided on the locations, click the <b>View Plan</b>
		to see or edit the plan that you have created.
	</p>
	<p class="answer">> Edit the plan to your needs by adding
		Transport, Accommodation and Agency.</p>
	<p class="answer">> You can also change the number of days and
		number of people who are joining you on your trip.</p>
	<p class="answer">
		> Click on <b>Save</b> to save your plan and also calculate your
		budget.
	</p>
	<p class="answer">> If the starting city is not Allepey, Goa,
		Kannyakumari, Ooty, Madurai or Manali, then the budget will not be
		calculated for the distance between two cities. In short, the
		application provides better results if you are traveling beteen these
		six cities</p>

	<h1 class="question">How to generate a plan for a specific number
		of days?</h1>
	<p class="answer">
		Of present, the application holds locations for a maximum 3 days of
		travel. Beyond which, locations can be expected to be added very soon.
		To generate a plan for a number of days enter the number of days in
		the form present in the home page and then click <b>Generate Plan</b>
	</p>

	<h1 class="question">Why are there only a few cities to access in
		the application?</h1>
	<p class="answer">
		Holiday Planner application is currently on its Snapshot version. More
		Cities will be added along the line of time. To see upcoming plans and
		packages, click on the <b>View All Packages</b> on the Home page.
	</p>

	<h1 class="question">How is the budget for the trip calculated?</h1>
	<p class="answer">The application uses parameters like distance
		between the two cities, the mode of Transport being used, the agency
		you choose to travel with, the number of people accompanying you and
		the Accommodations you choose to stay. Also a sum of 200 Rupees is
		added for each day of your travel</p>

	<h1 class="question">Why is there no option to give a Testimonial?</h1>
	<p class="answer">
		This is just the snapshot version of the application. This feature
		will be added soon. Until then, please send your feedbacks to <b>xxxxxxxx@gmail.com</b>
		Our social media accounts too have not been opened yet, and they will
		be in the near future.
	</p>

